release_note: Fix missing text entry
Fixes a problem with payments
Fixes layout issues on the Punkt Premium screen
Rotating the device does not close screen when writing a new story Some users faced a crash when opening the app this is now fixed
Improvements and bug fixes
Fix problem when creating a new story and adding a photo

Fixed a crash that was introduced in previous update You can now edit and delete custom reasons Keyboard isn t blocking the text field anymore when entering longer stories Additional language: Ukrainian many thanks to all the translators Date is correctly displayed when creating a new story sometimes a date in the past was selected
Thanks to our amazing contributors Punkt is now also available in the following languages: Portuguese Romanian Serbian Croatian Hungarian Finnish Happy journaling!
Punkt is now available in Romanian. Many thanks to all of you who helped translating the app and bringing it to even more people!

Thanks to so many incredibly helpful users who have helped translating the app we are proud that Punkt is now available in: Slovenian Polish Swedish Czech From now on you can also share Punkt Premium yearly and lifetime with your family. We have enabled family sharing in this update. Thanks again for your help.

Dear Punkt users this version finally brings Punkt to the iPad. Enjoy an experience fully optimized for the bigger screen. Additionally we have improved the tab bar for accessbility. We hope you enjoy this update! Many thanks for everyone who has helped testing the app before and provide incredibly helpful feedback.

Good morning everyone! The app is now available in Italian. We really want to thank everyone for the amazing and helpful feedback we are receiving. If you have a second it would be amazing if you could support the app by writing a short review on the App Store.

Good morning everyone! The app is now available in Italian. We really want to thank everyone for the amazing and helpful feedback we are receiving. If you have a second it would be amazing if you could support the app by writing a short review on the App Store.
Happy new year everyone! This release fixes a bug that prevented motivational quotes to be displayed. Thanks to everyone who reported this and reached out to us.

New languages: Russian and French Your support is incredible. Thanks to you Punkt is now available for even more people. Your feedback is so important to make the app better every day. If you like the app and have a minute please feel free to leave a review on the App Store. :
So many awesome people want to help us translate Punkt. We ve added languages that we are currently working on to the settings page.

Fix date picker issue on iOS 14. When changing the date of a story by tapping today the date picker is now optimised for iOS 14. Optimise date picker for setting reminders. A story can not be accidentally dismissed. App status setting shows you if your stories are being backed up in iCloud.

Fix crash when trying to export stories to CSV Fallback to passcode in case Face ID fails Adding new languages: Spanish and Dutch Many thanks to everyone who is giving such incredibly helpful feedback. Special thanks goes out to all contributors who helped to translate the app to Spanish and Dutch. We are so grateful!
Fixes a problem were motivation quotes were not loaded in German.
Your stories belong to you. Therefore we ve made it super easy to export them in a CSV file so you can store them wherever you want.

What s new: Custom reasons are finally there. You can now disable predefined reasons and create your own so you have more flexibility for creating your stories. You can now add a photo directly from your camera. Add more haptic feedback. In case there is a problem with your iCloud you can now see this in the settings screen. Bug fixes: Story overlay for photos in dark mode uses correct font colors.

Thanks to your great feedback we could improve the following in this update. Editing locations in past stories is now possible. Improved text visibility of stories with photo. You can perform a long press to see just the photo and hide the story. Bug fixes: Locations can now be reused for multiple stories.

Editing photos in the past is now possible If you had very quick fingers and selected a recent location super fast the app sometimes crashed. This is now fixed. As always thank you so much for your great feedback!
There was a little bug in the app that showed you a previous story when clicking Add new story from My Day screen.

Your incredible feedback helped us a lot to make major improvements for this update. You can now edit a story. Travel back in time and add a story for any previous day. Just in case you missed writing an entry. Long stories are no longer cut off every word counts and is precious. Locations can now be edited and changed. Location search includes all your recent locations to easily reuse frequently visited places.

As your privacy is of utmost importance we ve added Face ID or Touch ID to protect your stories. What else is in included in this update Better support for dynamic type on the statistics screen Text of a story can now be copied Thank you so much for your amazing feedback. This is incredibly helpful to make the app better day by day.

To be ready for the big wide world we ve made some accessibility improvements. Punkt now supports voice over and voice control. We are super excited that Punkt is finally available on the App Store. We really enjoy this special day with you. In that sense we have removed the paywall so you can see your insights for free.
